ISLAMABAD, Apr 06 (APP): Prime Minister Imran Khan on Tuesday appointed Senator Fida Muhammad as Pakistan Tehrik-e-Insaf (PTI) Chief Whip in Senate. He has also appointed Senator Ejaz Chaudhry as PTI’s Parliamentary Leader in the Upper House of Parliament.
